Interface GL10

All Superinterfaces:
GLCommon
All Known Subinterfaces:
GL11
public interface GL10
extends GLCommon

Interface wrapping all standard OpenGL ES 1.0 methods. Note that this excludes and fixed point OpenGL ES 1.0 methods!

Author:
